             (Police-constable E 9). I took the prisoner running, and have the cloth.</p>
               <p>MR. CULVERWELL. This is the cloth - I had placed it on the cutting-board just before I left it, to get my breakfast.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 21.</p>
